---
title: One-Pot Char Siu Beef Meatball & Noodle Soup with Green Beans
description: A fragrant noodle soup is exactly what you need in the cooler months to warm you up from the inside out. Beef meatballs,
infused with ginger and lemongrass, simmer in a flavour-packed broth with golden egg noodles and tender veggies. You’ll be slurping your way to happiness in no time!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66be974a3546b43b79d2ec67-5d679b53.jpeg
